Subject: [PATCH 1999/2508] ASoC: Intel: add fw name to common dsp context

commit 40c3ac46a49da3b01b1802eb4c4ff08626f48546 upstream

In order to pass the fw name to IPC driver for loading fw, we
need to add a memeber to store the fw name

